" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未來都唔會有啲咩特別既推廣活動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為已經做撚死左m記班人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至尊係我仲做緊個陣，每晚收夜必食<br />\n自己去拎塊肉煎，菜芝士蕃茄青瓜洋蔥都係全新鮮。諗起都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依嫁新個3樣，得個磨菇叫有睇題<br />\n安格斯牛喎⋯⋯足13g喎⋯⋯係咪呀</blockquote><br />\n依家個3個係咩 賣緊幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n安格斯聲稱130g未煎果陣 好似係<br />\n比起本身用果隻4:1肉 姐係大塊牛肉重10幾g<br />\n安格斯賣貴另外兩款2$<br />\n而定價係睇間舖既位置同埋成本去衡量<br />\n普遍都係35.8-37.8一個餐<br />\n呢啲冇乜點留意<br />\n個人覺得安格斯係幾正既<br />\n好似改厚左 肉汁多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外兩款食都唔敢食<br />\n因為小弟唔鍾意食菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5103caec2fb2560fc6223bc79c65dba2da1ffa32","tid":149811,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/013233_600d18d51daf10ea0397d96a9c5b51a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F013233_600d18d51daf10ea0397d96a9c5b51a5.jpg&h=22af6531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會係出呢隻<br />\n好似叫signature angus beef乜乜乜<br />\n利申外國</blockquote><br />\nFB好似就係宣傳緊呢款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個我覺得ok既 有兩款芝士 個辣醬都好正，番兜左兩次<br />\n個餐差唔多5x港紙，但係個咪道同質素係值呢個價<br />\n不過如果係香港出我就唔敢保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e716f88c8897715f756400e6d7bb1b5708928e53","tid":149811,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img 